// Phase 22 host-bridge showcase (not a shipped web app or game).
kośaḥ mārga-saṃyojane.
sthāpanam mārga-saṃyojane /users/{id} vākyam user_show iti.
āhvānam std.web.route_match vākyam /users/108 iti mārga-saṃyojane phalaṃ nidadhāti.
āhvānam std.serialize vākyam json iti phalaṃ darśayati.

samūhalakṣaṇaḥ citra-saṃkhyāḥ eka dve trīṇi catvāri pañca.
āhvānam std.plot.sparkline citra-saṃkhyāḥ darśayati.
āhvānam std.data.describe citra-saṃkhyāḥ phalaṃ nidadhāti.
gaṇakaḥ phalaṃ darśayati.
